    #Sports Highlights
Sports Highlights is a web application that provides high-quality video highlights of various sports matches. Users can sign up and sign in to search and watch their favorite sports highlights.

                  #Features
Users can create an account with their email and password, and log in to access the content.
Users can search for specific games by name.
Video Highlights are categorized by sports leagues such as Premier League, La Liga, Champions League, and Europa League.

                     #Tech Stack
HTML/CSS for the structure and styling of the website.
JavaScript for the dynamic behavior of the website.
Bootstrap for responsive design and prebuilt components.
JSON Server to simulate a REST API for user data and video content.


                 #Folder Structure

index.html: The main HTML file for the website.
css/style.css: The CSS file for styling the website.
js/script.js: The JavaScript file for dynamic functionality.
db.json: The JSON file that acts as a mock database for users and video data.

                    #Usage
Sign Up
Click on the "Sign Up" button in the navbar.
Enter your email and password.
Click "Sign Up" to create your account.
Sign In
Click on the "Sign In" button in the navbar.
Enter your email and password.
Click "Sign In" to log in to your account.
Search for Videos
Use the search bar in the navbar to search for specific games by name (e.g., "Mancity" or "Tottenham").
The search results will display the matching videos.
Browse Videos by Category
Use the navbar links to browse videos by category (All, Premier League, La Liga, Champions League, Europa League).
Click on a category to view the videos.

